text: Florida's 1st congressional district is a congressional district in the U.S. state of Florida. It is in the state's western Panhandle. It includes all of Escambia, Okaloosa, Santa Rosa, and Walton counties and portions of Holmes county. The district is currently represented by Republican Matt Gaetz. ==Election results== ==References== Category:Government of Florida Category:Congressional districts of Florida
